Thank you for your interest in contributing to TestORE! 🎉
🤝 How to Contribute
Reporting Bugs
Found a bug? Please report it!

Check existing issues first
Create a new issue with:

Clear title
Description of the problem
Steps to reproduce
Expected vs actual behavior
Your environment (OS, Rust version, etc.)
Error messages/logs



Suggesting Features
Have an idea? We'd love to hear it!

Check if it's already suggested
Create an issue with:

Feature description
Use case/motivation
Proposed implementation (optional)



Pull Requests
Setup
bash# Fork and clone
git clone https://github.com/YOUR_USERNAME/testore.git
cd testore

# Create branch
git checkout -b feature/your-feature-name

# Make changes
# ...

# Test
cargo test
cargo clippy
cargo fmt --check

# Commit
git commit -m "feat: your feature description"

# Push
git push origin feature/your-feature-name
Guidelines

Code Style: Follow Rust conventions, run cargo fmt
Tests: Add tests for new features
Documentation: Update README/docs as needed
Commit Messages: Use conventional commits format

feat: new feature
fix: bug fix
docs: documentation
test: tests
chore: maintenance



Review Process

Submit PR with clear description
Maintainers will review
Address feedback
Get approval
Merge! 🎉

🔧 Development
Building
bashcargo build --release
Testing
bash# Run all tests
cargo test

# Run specific test
cargo test test_name

# Run with output
cargo test -- --nocapture
Linting
bash# Check code
cargo clippy

# Format code
cargo fmt
Local Testing
bash# Start local validator
solana-test-validator

# Deploy locally
anchor deploy --provider.cluster localnet

# Test CLI
./target/release/testore --rpc http://localhost:8899 mine
📋 Project Structure
testore/
├── programs/
│   └── testore-program/  # Anchor smart contract
│       ├── src/
│       │   └── lib.rs     # Main program logic
│       └── Cargo.toml
├── cli/
│   ├── src/
│   │   ├── main.rs        # CLI entry point
│   │   ├── miner.rs       # Mining engine
│   │   ├── proof.rs       # PoW logic
│   │   └── leaderboard.rs # Stats fetching
│   └── Cargo.toml
├── bridge/
│   ├── src/
│   │   └── main.rs        # Airdrop bridge
│   └── Cargo.toml
├── tests/
│   └── integration_test.rs
└── web/
    └── index.html         # Browser miner
🎯 Good First Issues
Looking for something to work on?

Add GPU mining support
Improve error messages
Add more tests
Optimize mining algorithm
Improve documentation
Add metrics/monitoring
Create Discord bot

Check issues labeled good-first-issue.
🚀 Release Process
(For maintainers)

Update version in Cargo.toml
Update CHANGELOG.md
Create git tag: git tag v0.x.0
Push: git push origin v0.x.0
GitHub Actions will build and release

📝 Code of Conduct
Our Pledge
We pledge to make participation a harassment-free experience for everyone.
Standards
✅ Do:

Be respectful
Welcome newcomers
Give constructive feedback
Accept criticism gracefully

❌ Don't:

Harass or insult
Post inappropriate content
Share private information
Act unprofessionally
